/>\n利申: 食住煙回</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你成功得一次 就會第二次<br />\n朋友因素影響好大<br />\n<br />\n唔好比藉口自己咪得lo<br />\ne.g:有真普選我就戒煙"},{"pid":"f811b54899c4c7c00cdf6715c3c88c3c514abed0","tid":171112,"uid":94338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T06:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒左半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁wo <br />\n想食煙果時做咩頂住好"},{"pid":"68dccaf2bc4ea36f0a1f27aa38fc962db98a00a6","tid":171112,"uid":81213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:13:22.000Z","msg":"食咗十年 戒咗年幾 頭一兩個禮拜最辛苦 喺街聞到二手煙都會索大啖啲"}]}